      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $n,p \\in \\N^*$ et $\\mathbb{U}_n$ le groupe des racines $n$-{\\`e}mes de 1.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n,p \\in \\N^*\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathbb{U}_n\\)</span> le groupe des racines <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>-<span>è</span>mes de 1.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "fd3cb9ca-8c84-4563-9629-d013dd96508e",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{x \\in \\mathbb{U}_n} x^p$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{x \\in \\mathbb{U}_n} x^p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9f6bc6a3-e505-49bc-8798-72ecc717f5ff",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum=n$ si $p\\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, n)$, 0 sinon.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum=n\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p\\not\\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, n)\\)</span>, 0 sinon.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1d111167-42aa-4f21-add8-de4a60679671",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $P$ un polyn{\\^o}me {\\`a} coefficients complexes de degr{\\'e} inf{\\'e}rieur ou {\\'e}gal\n    {\\`a} $n-1$ et $M = \\max\\{|P(x)|,\\ x \\in\\mathbb{U}_n\\}$.\n    Montrer que tous les coefficients de $P$ sont born{\\'e}s par $M$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P\\)</span> un polyn<span>ô</span>me <span>à</span> coefficients complexes de degr<span>é</span> inf<span>é</span>rieur ou <span>é</span>gal <span>à</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n-1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M = \\max\\{|P(x)|,\\ x \\in\\mathbb{U}_n\\}\\)</span>. Montrer que tous les coefficients de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P\\)</span> sont born<span>é</span>s par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4eac84af-c9bc-435c-983d-be1b6c2abd59",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a_k = \\sum_{x\\in\\mathbb{U}_n} \\frac {P(x)}{nx^k}$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_k = \\sum_{x\\in\\mathbb{U}_n} \\frac {P(x)}{nx^k}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
